  sugar: 39 g
  protein: 32 g
  fiber: 6 g
  sodium: 460 mg
time required: 45 minutes
servings: 2
author: Michelle Doll Olson
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/pork-bulgogi-meatballs-5c1157cfe3f33906126b9672
cuisine: Korean
